SENATE FILE NO. SF0103
Terminating and defunding diversity, equity and inclusion.
Sponsored by: Senator(s) Steinmetz, Boner, Hicks, Hutchings
and Jones and Representative(s) Angelos,
Haroldson, Lawley, Neiman and Smith, S
A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to the administration of the government;
2 generally prohibiting diversity, equity and inclusion
3 efforts and mandates by state agencies and educational
4 institutions; conditioning the expenditure of appropriated
5 funds as specified; specifying applicability; and providing
6 for an effective date.
7
8 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
9
10 Section 1. W.S. 9-2-1014.4 and 21-16-2001 are created
11 to read:
12
13 9-2-1014.4. Funds and expenditures for diversity,
14 equity and inclusion efforts prohibited.
15
