2025 STATE OF WYOMING 25LSO-0501
1 receive a grade includes content on diversity, equity and
2 inclusion or critical race theory;
3
4 (iv) "Related practice":
5
6 (A) Includes any requirement or guidance
7 that a course instructor include or curate materials on the
8 basis of race, sex or gender dysphonia;
9
10 (B) Includes participating in any workshop,
11 training, seminar or professional development on any
12 related content;
13
14 (C) Does not include any programming
15 explicitly required by, and limited to, the institutional
16 obligations to comply with state or federal law or an
17 applicable court order.
18
19 (b) In prescribing the studies to be pursued at the
20 University of Wyoming or a Wyoming community college, the
21 board of trustees of the University of Wyoming and the
22 district boards of each community college shall establish
23 curricula and designate courses in a manner that does not
9 SF0103

