5 requirements, subject to subsection (d) of this section.
6
7 (c) The board of trustees of the University of
8 Wyoming and the district boards of each community college,
9 or any employee or professional thereof, shall not require,
10 solicit or incentivize faculty or students to apply or
11 participate in related practices, or include related
12 content in any course, as a condition of approval,
13 designation or listing as part of any academic degree
14 program, including general education, major, minor or
15 certificate requirements or as a condition of consideration
