17 salary adjustment or any other incentive, subject to
18 subsection (d) of this section.
19
20 (d) Academic degree program requirements of any
21 major, minor, certificate or department whose title clearly
22 establishes its course of study as primarily focused on
23 racial, ethnic or gender studies may be exempted from the
10 SF0103

2025 STATE OF WYOMING 25LSO-0501
1 requirements of subsections (a) and (b) of this section in
2 writing by the board of trustees or the district board, as
3 applicable, subject to the following:
