5 (i) No student shall be required or constrained
6 to enroll in any exempted program, department or course to
7 satisfy the requirements of any other academic degree
8 program, including general education requirements or any
9 other major, minor or certificate requirements;
10
11 (ii) Courses offered or listed by or under
